g the Core\" href=\"/blog/portfolio-site-2\">Read more<svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"w-6 flex-none fill-current\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M24 3 18 .5v2H0v1h18v2L24 3Z\"></path></svg><span class=\"absolute inset-0\"></span></a></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article><div class=\"relative flex flex-col items-start pl-8 relative before:absolute after:absolute before:bg-[var(--theme-text-muted)] after:bg-[var(--theme-border-subtle)] before:top-0 before:left-0 before:h-6 before:w-px after:top-8 after:bottom-0 after:left-0 after:w-px\"><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\">Portfolio Site Rebuild — Part 3: Features, Polish &amp; Deployment</h3><time dateTime=\"2025\" class=\"order-first text-sm text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\">2025</time><p class=\"mt-2.5 text-base text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\">Adding Pagefind search, table of contents, dark/light theme, copy-to-clipboard, PWA support, security headers, RSS feed, dynamic OG images, View Transitions, and deploying to Cloudflare Pages.</p><a class=\"mt-6 flex gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)] transition hover:text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\" aria-label=\"Read more: Portfolio Site Rebuild — Part 3: Features, Polish &amp; Deployment\" href=\"/blog/portfolio-site-3\">Read more<svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"w-6 flex-none fill-current\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M24 3 18 .5v2H0v1h18v2L24 3Z\"></path></svg><span class=\"absolute inset-0\"></span></a></div></article></div></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 mt-12 w-full sm:mt-16 lg:mt-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-x-12 gap-y-8\"><nav><div class=\"font-display text