loud-resume-challenge\",\"children\":\"Cloud Resume Challenge\"}],\" — static HTML on S3, CloudFront in front, Lambda visitor counter in back. It proved I could build on AWS, but a single-page resume doesn't scale into a portfolio. I needed project pages, build logs, and room to grow.\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"requirements\",\"children\":\"Requirements\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Before picking tools, I defined what the new site had to do:\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",\"$L17\",\"\\n\",\"$L18\",\"\\n\",\"$L19\",\"\\n\",\"$L1a\",\"\\n\",\"$L1b\",\"\\n\",\"$L1c\",\"\\n\",\"$L1d\",\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",\"$L1e\",\"\\n\",\"$L1f\",\"\\n\",\"$L20\",\"\\n\",\"$L21\",\"\\n\",\"$L22\",\"\\n\",\"$L23\",\"\\n\",\"$L24\",\"\\n\",\"$L25\",\"\\n\",\"$L26\",\"\\n\",\"$L27\",\"\\n\",\"$L28\",\"\\n\",\"$L29\",\"\\n\",\"$L2a\",\"\\n\",\"$L2b\",\"\\n\",\"$L2c\",\"\\n\",\"$L2d\",\"\\n\",\"$L2e\",\"\\n\",\"$L2f\",\"\\n\",\"$L30\",\"\\n\",\"$L31\",\"\\n\",\"$L32\",\"\\n\",\"$L33\",\"\\n\",\"$L34\",\"\\n\",\"\\n\"]}]}]]}]}]]}]}],\"$L35\"]\n36:I[3425,[\"2441\",\"static/chunks/2441-896cb9e17806853d.js\",\"2619\",\"static/chunks/2619-8d0937a46481eb03.js\",\"7334\",\"static/chunks/7334-561dd51b111b9634.js\",\"9838\",\"static/chunks/app/blog/portfolio-site-1/page-253f073c507ccdc9.js\"],\"CodeBlock\"]\n37:I[2737,[\"2441\",\"static/chunks/2441-896cb9e17806853d.js\",\"2619\",\"static/chunks/2619-8d0937a46481eb03.js\",\"7334\",\"static/chunks/7334-561dd51b111b9634.js\",\"9838\",\"static/chunks/app/blog/portfolio-site-1/page-253f073c507ccdc9.js\"],\"GridPattern\"]\n38:I[4566,[\"2441\",\"static/chunks/2441-896cb9e17806853d.js\",\"2619\",\"static/chunks/2619-8d0937a46481eb03.js\",\"7334\",\"static/chunks/7334-561dd51b111b9634.js\",\"9838\",\"static/chunks/app/blog/portfolio-site-1/page-253f073c507ccdc9.js\"],\"FadeInStagger\"]\n17:[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Project showcase\"}],\" — Individual pages with architecture diagrams, code snippets, and repo links\"]}]\n18:[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Blog / build logs\"}],\" — Long-form technical posts with Markdown and syntax highlighting\"]}]\n19:[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Search\"}],\" — Users should be able to find content without browsing every page\"]}]\n1a:[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Fast and free\"}],\" — Static generation, global CDN, no server costs\"]}]\n1b:[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Easy to update\"}],\" — Drop in a file, push, deployed. No touching application code to add content\"]}]\n1c:[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Clean design\"}],\" — Dark theme, minimal, animations that don't get in the way\"]}]\n1d:[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Future-proof\"}],\" — Modern tooling that won't need a rewrite in a year\"]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"framework-nextjs-15\",\"children\":\"Framework: Next.js 15\"}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"I looked at Astro, Gatsby, Hugo, and Next.js. Each has trade-offs:\"}]\n20:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"my-10 max-sm:-mx-6 max-sm:flex max-sm:overflow-x-auto\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-sm:min-w-full max-sm:flex-none max-sm:px-6\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"table\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"thead\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"children\":\"Framework\"}],[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"children\":\"Strength\"}],[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"children\":\"Why I Passed\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"tbody\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"Astro\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"Great for content sites\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"Island architecture felt like an unnecessary constraint for React components\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"Gatsby\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"Powerful plugin ecosystem\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"Too much GraphQL ceremony for a portfolio\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"Hugo / 11ty\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"Blazing fast builds\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"No component-based layouts, limited React ecosystem\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Next.js 15\"}]}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"App Router, RSC, MDX\"}]}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Won — static gen + React + mature ecosystem\"}]}]]}]]}]]}]}]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Next.js gave me static generation for performance, React Server Components for flexibility, and file-based routing that maps cleanly to a content site. The experimental View Transitions API support was a bonus — native browser page transitions without extra JavaScript.\"}]\n22:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"styling-tailwind-css-v4\",\"children\":\"Styling: Tailwind CSS v4\"}]\n23:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Tailwind v4 dropped the JavaScript config file entirely. Everything lives in CSS now:\"}]\n24:[\"$\",\"$L36\",null,{\"className\":\"shiki nord\",\"style\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#2e3440ff\",\"color\":\"#d8dee9ff\"},\"tabIndex\":\"0\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"line\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#81A1C1\"},\"children\":\"@import\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#ECEFF4\"},\"children\":\" \\\"\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#A3BE8C\"},\"children\":\"tailwindcss\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#ECEFF4\"},\"children\":\"\\\"\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#81A1C1\"},\"children\":\";\"}]]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"line\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"line\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#81A1C1\"},\"children\":\"@theme\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#ECEFF4\"},\"children\":\" {\"}]]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"line\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#D8DEE9FF\"},\"children\":\"  --font-display: \\\"Mona Sans\\\"\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#ECEFF4\"},\"children\":\",\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#81A1C1\"},\"children\":\" ui-sans-serif\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#ECEFF4\"},\"children\":\",\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#81A1C1\"},\"children\":\" system-ui\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#ECEFF4\"},\"children\":\",\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#81A1C1\"},\"children\":\" sans-serif\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#D8DEE9FF\"},\"children\":\";\"}]]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"line\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#D8DEE9FF\"},\"children\":\"  --color-neutral-950: \"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#ECEFF4\"},\"children\":\"#\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#D8DEE9\"},\"children\":\"0a0a0a\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#D8DEE9FF\"},\"children\":\";\"}]]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"line\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"#D8DEE9FF\"},\"children\":\"}\"}]}]]}]}]\n25:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"One \",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"@theme\"}],\" block holds all design tokens — colors, fonts, spacing. No jumping between files. The \",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"@import \\\"tailwindcss\\\"\"}],\" entry point replaces the old \",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"@tailwind base/components/utilities\"}],\" directives.\"]}]\n26:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"content-mdx\",\"children\":\"Content: MDX\"}]\n27:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"MDX is Markdown with JSX support. Content lives in the repo alongside code — version-controlled, no external CMS, no API calls at build time. The processing pipeline:\"}]\n28:[\"$\",\"$L36\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"MDX → Zod Validation → remarkGfm → remarkMDXLayout → rehypeSlug → rehypeShiki → rehypeUnwrapImages → HTML\\n\"}]}]\n29:[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Zod\"}],\" — Schema validation on every metadata export at build time\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"remarkGfm\"}],\" — Tables, task lists, autolinks\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"rehypeSlug\"}],\" — Generates heading IDs for anchor links and table of contents\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"rehypeShiki\"}],\" — Syntax highlighting with the \",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"github-dark\"}],\" theme\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"rehypeUnwrapImages\"}],\" — Full-width images instead of paragraph-wrapped\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Custom layout plugin\"}],\" — Automatic layout wrapping per page\"]}],\"\\n\"]}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"hosting-cloudflare-pages\",\"children\":\"Hosting: Cloudflare Pages\"}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The old S3 + CloudFront + Route 53 stack worked but was heavy for a static site. DNS was already on Cloudflare, making Pages the natural choice:\"}]\n2c:[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Free tier with unlimited bandwidth and 500 builds/month\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Connect a GitHub repo, set the build command, auto-deploy on push\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Custom domain setup was a single click since DNS was already there\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Preview deployments on every pull request\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Built-in Web Analytics — privacy-first, no cookies, just a script tag\"}],\"\\n\"]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"animations-framer-motion--view-transitions\",\"children\":\"Animations: Framer Motion + View Transitions\"}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Framer Motion handles scroll-triggered fade-ins and staggered card reveals. The \",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"useInView\"}],\" hook makes it declarative — wrap a component, define the animation, done. No imperative scroll listeners or intersection observer boilerplate.\"]}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"For page-to-page navigation, the View Transitions API handles smooth crossfade transitions natively in the browser. Next.js 15 supports it as an experimental flag — one line in the config, a few CSS keyframes, and pages transition smoothly. It respects \",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"prefers-reduced-motion\"}],\" automatically.\"]}]\n30:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"project-structure\",\"children\":\"Project Structure\"}]\n31:[\"$\",\"$L36\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"src/\\n  app/\\n    page.tsx                 # Homepage\\n    about/page.tsx           # About page\\n    blog/[slug]/page.mdx     # Blog posts\\n    projects/[slug]/page.mdx # Project pages\\n    experience/[slug]/       # Experience detail pages\\n    feed.xml/route.ts        # RSS feed\\n  components/\\n    layout/                  # RootLayout, Navigation, Footer\\n    sections/                # Hero, About, Projects, FeaturedPosts\\n    SearchDialog.tsx          # Pagefind search modal\\n    TableOfContents.tsx       # Auto-generated heading nav\\n  data/                      # Structured experience and skills data\\n  lib/\\n    mdx.ts                   # MDX loader with Zod validation\\n    readingTime.ts           # Word count → reading time\\n\"}]}]\n32:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Each blog post and project gets its own directory. The MDX file exports metadata (title, date, tags) and the content body. A loader in \",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"lib/mdx.ts\"}],\" uses \",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"fast-glob\"}],\" to discover files, validates metadata with Zod, and sorts by date.\"]}]\n33:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"next-up\",\"children\":\"Next Up\"}]\n34:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Stack is locked in, dependencies installed. \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"/blog/portfolio-site-2\",\"children\":\"Part 2\"}],\" covers building the component library, wiring up the MDX pipeline with Zod validation, and laying out the homepage.\"]}]\n35:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"relative pt-12 sm:pt-16 lg:pt-20 mt-12 sm:mt-16 lg:mt-20\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"absolute inset-x-0 top-0 -z-10 h-[884px] overflow-hidden rounded-t-4xl bg-linear-to-b from-[var(--theme-bg-elevated)]\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L37\",null,{\"className\":\"absolute inset-0 h-full w-full [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_bottom_left,white_40%,transparent_50%)] fill-[var(--theme-bg-elevated)] stroke-[var(--theme-border-subtle)]\",\"yOffset\":-270}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L7\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-2xl\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":[\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"block font-display tracking-tight text-[var(--theme-text-primary)] [text-wrap:balance] text-2xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"More articles\"}]]}],\"$undefined\"]}]}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 mt-16\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L38\",null,{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L7\",\"/blog/portfolio-site-2\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"article\",\"/blog/portfolio-site-2\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"relative flex flex-col items-start pl-8 relative before:absolute after:absolute before:bg-[var(--theme-text-muted)] after:bg-[var(--theme-border-subtle)] before:top-0 before:left-0 before:h-6 before:w-px after:top-8 after:bottom-0 after:left-0 after:w-px\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Portfolio Site Rebuild — Part 2: Building the Core\"}],[\"$\",\"time\",null,{\"dateTime\":\"2025\",\"className\":\"order-first text-sm text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\",\"children\":\"2025\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2.5 text-base text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\",\"children\":\"Setting up the Next.js project, building the component library, wiring up MDX with Zod validation, and designing the homepage layout.\"}],[\"$\",\"$L9\",null,{\"href\":\"/blog/portfolio-site-2\",\"className\":\"mt-6 flex gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)] transition hover:text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\",\"aria-label\":\"Read more: Portfolio Site Rebuild — Part 2: Building the Core\",\"children\":[\"Read more\",[\"$\",\"svg\",null,{\"viewBox\":\"0 0 24 6\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\",\"className\":\"w-6 flex-none fill-current\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"path\",null,{\"fillRule\":\"evenodd\",\"clipRule\":\"evenodd\",\"d\":\"M24 3 18 .5v2H0v1h18v2L24 3Z\"}]}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"absolute inset-0\"}]]}]]}]}]]}],[\"$\",\"$L7\",\"/blog/portfolio-site-3\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"article\",\"/blog/portfolio-site-3\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"relative flex flex-col items-start pl-8 relative before:absolute after:absolute before:bg-[var(--theme-text-muted)] after:bg-[var(--theme-border-subtle)] before:top-0 before:left-0 before:h-6 before:w-px after:top-8 after:bottom-0 after:left-0 after:w-px\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Portfolio Site Rebuild — Part 3: Features, Polish & Deployment\"}],[\"$\",\"time\",null,{\"dateTime\":\"2025\",\"className\":\"order-first text-sm text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\",\"children\":\"2025\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2.5 text-base text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\",\"children\":\"Adding Pagefind search, table of contents, dark/light theme, copy-to-clipboard, PWA support, security headers, RSS feed, dynamic OG images, View Transitions, and deploying to Cloudflare Pages.\"}],[\"$\",\"$L9\",null,{\"href\":\"/blog/portfolio-site-3\",\"className\":\"mt-6 flex gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)] transition hover:text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\",\"aria-label\":\"Read more: Portfolio Site Rebuild — Part 3: Features, Polish & Deployment\",\"children\":[\"Read more\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\"]}]]}]}]]}]]}]}]}]]}]\n39:[\"$\",\"svg\",null,{\"viewBox\":\"0 0 24 6\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\",\"className\":\"w-6 flex-none fill-current\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"path\",null,{\"fillRule\":\"evenodd\",\"clipRule\":\"evenodd\",\"d\":\"M24 3 18 .5v2H0v1h18v2L24 3Z\"}]}]\n3a:[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"absolute inset-0\"}]\n"}